      "text": "So here's the mental shit."
    },
    {
      "start": 1.32,
      "end": 3.64,
      "text": "You don't patch socks because socks got cheap."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.28,
      "end": 6.36,
      "text": "The economics made patching irrational."
    },
    {
      "start": 8.64,
      "end": 9.66,
      "text": "Code just got that cheap."
    },
    {
      "start": 11.02,
      "end": 12.22,
      "text": "Prompts in code intent."
    },
    {
      "start": 13.28,
      "end": 14.74,
      "text": "Tests preserve behavior."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.16,
      "end": 17.82,
      "text": "Grounding maintained style."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.92,
      "end": 21.88,
      "text": "Code is generated, verified and disposable."
    },
    {
      "start": 23.6,
      "end": 25.28,
      "text": "The code is just plastic."
    },
    {
